OL,3,CKneecap are 'completely intolerable'
OL,4,Csays Keir Starmer
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister has said what Irish
OL,7,Flanguage rap trio Kneecap stand for
OL,8,Fand say is "completely intolerable".
OL,10,FSir Keir Starmer said the Crown
OL,11,FProsecution Service (CPS) would be
OL,12,Flooking at a judgment that a member of
OL,13,Fthe group will not face a terror trial
OL,14,F"very carefully".
OL,26,@pD@LOUpD@cO]vD@AOUvD@PO]
