FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773342676
OL,3,CKneecap are 'completely intolerable'
OL,4,Csays Keir Starmer
OL,6,FThe CPS appealed against the decision
OL,7,Fat the High Court at a hearing in
OL,8,FJanuary, with the Kneecap rapper
OL,9,Fopposing the challenge.
OL,11,FIn a judgment on Wednesday, two judges
OL,12,Fat the High Court upheld the decision
OL,13,Fand dismissed the CPS appeal.
OL,15,FJudge Goldspring had agreed with O
OL,16,FhAnnaidh's lawyers that prosecutors
OL,17,Fneeded to seek the Attorney General's
OL,18,Fpermission to charge the rapper before
OL,19,Finforming him on May 21 that he would
OL,20,Fbe charged with a terror offence.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
