FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773342676
OL,3,CKneecap are 'completely intolerable'
OL,4,Csays Keir Starmer
OL,6,FThis permission was sought and given
OL,7,Fthe following day, which the court
OL,8,Fheard meant the charge fell outside
OL,9,Fthe six-month time frame in which
OL,10,Fcriminal charges against a defendant
OL,11,Fcan be brought.
OL,13,FAsked during a visit to Belfast about
OL,14,Fthe decision to bring the case against
OL,15,Fthe group member, Sir Keir said: "My
OL,16,Fviews on Kneecap are very well known
OL,17,Fin relation to what they stand for and
OL,18,Fwhat they say, which is completely
OL,19,Fintolerable.
OL,26,@wD@bOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
