PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773342676
OL,3,CKneecap are 'completely intolerable'
OL,4,Csays Keir Starmer
OL,6,F"I think the CPS were obviously
OL,7,Fsubject to the High Court decision and
OL,8,Fthey will be looking at the judgment
OL,9,Fvery carefully."
OL,11,FIn a statement released after the
OL,12,Fjudgment on Wednesday, O hAnnaidh
OL,13,Fsaid: "This entire process was never
OL,14,Fabout me, never about any threat to
OL,15,Fthe public and never about
OL,16,F'terrorism', a word used by the
OL,17,FBritish Government to discredit people
OL,18,Fyou oppress both in Ireland and across
OL,19,Fthe world.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@PO]uD@GOU
