OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773342676
OL,3,CKneecap are 'completely intolerable'
OL,4,Csays Keir Starmer
OL,6,F"It was always about Palestine and
OL,7,Fabout what happens if you dare to
OL,8,Fspeak up. About what happens if you
OL,9,Fcan reach large groups of people and
OL,10,Fexpose their hypocrisy.
OL,12,F"I will not be silent. Kneecap will
OL,13,Fnot be silent."
